      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW REVY (2) won again and recorded an impressive time after leading to make it two on end at Shepparton over 450m (25.36). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Sure to prove hard to beat. ONYX LASS (7) was well off top last time, finishing 5th (25.62) in a R/A FIN at Warrnambool. Great record here at the trip having never missed the frame including two wins. Won at her only start from this box. Leading chance. SIR SILVERTREE (3) scored two back in one of the fastest times of the program when on speed but last start drifted back and wound up strongly to finish a 5.5 lengths third at Bendigo (24.13). Can feature again. REUBEN HILL (8) must be included in calculations.",
